data_extraction_properties.name: location
data_extraction_properties.description: City or venue name where the shoot will take place

data_extraction_properties.name: shootType
data_extraction_properties.description: Type of shoot: wedding, portrait, engagement, event, product, or other

data_extraction_properties.name: mood
data_extraction_properties.description: 2-3 mood descriptors separated by commas (e.g., 'romantic, candid')

data_extraction_properties.name: primarySubjectNames
data_extraction_properties.description: Names of main subjects separated by commas

data_extraction_properties.name: primarySubjectRelationship
data_extraction_properties.description: Relationship of primary subjects: couple, family, individual, or group

data_extraction_properties.name: secondarySubjectsPresent
data_extraction_properties.description: Whether there are secondary subjects (pets, family, etc.)

data_extraction_properties.name: secondarySubjectsDetails
data_extraction_properties.description: Details about secondary subjects if present

data_extraction_properties.name: locationPreference
data_extraction_properties.description: Location preference: clustered (close together) or itinerary (spread out)

data_extraction_properties.name: mustHaveShots
data_extraction_properties.description: Specific requested shots separated by semicolons

data_extraction_properties.name: specialRequirements
data_extraction_properties.description: Special requirements like permits, props, or equipment

data_extraction_properties.name: experience
data_extraction_properties.description: Photographer experience level: beginner, intermediate, or professional
